Description: The name of the event that triggered this Webhook Notification
The ID of the event that triggered this Webhook Notification
The UTC time (formatted as an HTTP date) when the the event that triggered this Webhook Notification fired.
The list of Global Variables that are in scope for the element that fired the Event that triggered this Webhook Notification. The list may vary depending on the Event.
The internal ID of the Webhook configuration that triggered this Webhook Notification.
The internal ID of the webhook endpoint the Webhook Notification is sent to.
